When it comes to land investment and development, it goes without saying that Lagos is one of the most appreciable places to buy, invest and make huge returns on your investment. A market trend on the popular real estate site, Nigria Property Centre, bears out this fact.

It is also evident that for the discerning investor, what is paramount is massive and optimal returns on any land investment made and when you come to Lagos, the best place to achieve massive growth in your land portfolio is Ibeju Lekki. Presently called the New Lagos, Ibeju Lekki is poised to become the most developed area in West Africa with the huge potential to be one of the best real estate decision you will ever make as countless developments are presently coming up within the axis.

King’s Gate 2 thus offers you the opportunity to key into the massive potentials in the Ibeju Lekki sector as it is a developed estate located at Imosan off Igbogun, via La Campaign Tropicana Resort, Free Trade Zone, Ibeju Lekki, Lagos with close proximity to The Dangote Refinery, Lekki Deep Seaport, La Campaign Tropicana, Lekki Golf Course, Alaro City, Eleganza Industries, Pan Atlantic University, Markets, Filling Stations and various other developments.

The Estate neighbourhood is presently populated with pockets of dwellers and investors readily building their properties. The estate is a prime land that will position your land portfolio for the next wave of dwellers and homeowners that are coming down to the area considering the economic catalysts within the Free Trade Zone axis such as the Dangote Refinery, Lekki Deep Sea Port, The Eleganza Industries, Alaro City and The New International Airport.

Presently called the New Lagos, Ibeju Lekki is poised to become the most developed area in West Africa with the huge potential to be one of the best real estate decision you will ever make as countless developments are presently coming up within the axis.

King’s Gate 2 thus offers you the opportunity to key into the massive potentials in the Ibeju Lekki sector as it is a developed estate located at Imosan off Igbogun, via La Campaign Tropicana Resort, Free Trade Zone, Ibeju Lekki, Lagos with close proximity to The Dangote Refinery, Lekki Deep Seaport, La Campaign Tropicana, Lekki Golf Course, Alaro City, Eleganza Industries, Pan Atlantic University, Markets, Filling Stations and various other developments.

detail_description:
Serenity Gardens Estate 2 is a developed estate located inside Epe main Town in a very serene environment with close proximity to Epe Spa and Resorts, Alaro City, banks, markets, schools and various other developments. Some of the features of this amazing vicinity includes; Tarred roads, street light, clean portable water, drainage systems, perimeter fencing and a host of central sewage systems. Serenity Gardens set a high level benchmark in service delivery, infrastructures, eco-friendliness, functionality and loftiness. Saddled with Individual housing typologies of contemporary architecture.

The demographics of the area include a majority of Yoruba speaking natives, and people from different parts of the country living, working and doing business in the area. Epe town has potential for tourism as it is endowed with beautiful lagoon views and ocean fronts that will marvel your sight. The area is fast developing as investors and prospective land buyers are already building their homes and properties rapidly being one of the reasons why lands are constantly appreciating fast in the area.

Epe main town is a central hub for business, manufacturing, warehousing, and logistics. Forecasts have been made about an increase in commercial activities in this city as a result of these developments which will create thousands of jobs in the earnest future.

detail_description:
Serenity Gardens Estate 2 is a developed estate located inside Epe main Town in a very serene environment with close proximity to Epe Spa and Resorts, Alaro City, banks, markets, schools and various other developments. Some of the features of this amazing vicinity includes; Tarred roads, street light, clean portable water, drainage systems, perimeter fencing and a host of central sewage systems. Serenity Gardens set a high level benchmark in service delivery, infrastructures, eco-friendliness, functionality and loftiness. Saddled with Individual housing typologies of contemporary architecture.

The demographics of the area include a majority of Yoruba speaking natives, and people from different parts of the country living, working and doing business in the area. Epe town has potential for tourism as it is endowed with beautiful lagoon views and ocean fronts that will marvel your sight. The area is fast developing as investors and prospective land buyers are already building their homes and properties rapidly being one of the reasons why lands are constantly appreciating fast in the area.

Epe main town is a central hub for business, manufacturing, warehousing, and logistics. Forecasts have been made about an increase in commercial activities in this city as a result of these developments which will create thousands of jobs in the earnest future.

detail_description:
When it comes to land investment and development, it goes without saying that Lagos is one of the most appreciable places to buy, invest and make huge returns on your investment. A market trend on the popular real estate site, Nigria Property Centre, bears out this fact.

It is also evident that for the discerning investor, what is paramount is massive and optimal returns on any land investment made and when you come to Lagos, the best place to achieve massive growth in your land portfolio is Ibeju Lekki. Presently called the New Lagos, Ibeju Lekki is poised to become the most developed area in West Africa with the huge potential to be one of the best real estate decision you will ever make as countless developments are presently coming up within the axis.

King’s Gate 2 thus offers you the opportunity to key into the massive potentials in the Ibeju Lekki sector as it is a developed estate located at Imosan off Igbogun, via La Campaign Tropicana Resort, Free Trade Zone, Ibeju Lekki, Lagos with close proximity to The Dangote Refinery, Lekki Deep Seaport, La Campaign Tropicana, Lekki Golf Course, Alaro City, Eleganza Industries, Pan Atlantic University, Markets, Filling Stations and various other developments.

The Estate neighbourhood is presently populated with pockets of dwellers and investors readily building their properties. The estate is a prime land that will position your land portfolio for the next wave of dwellers and homeowners that are coming down to the area considering the economic catalysts within the Free Trade Zone axis such as the Dangote Refinery, Lekki Deep Sea Port, The Eleganza Industries, Alaro City and The New International Airport.

detail_description:
Serenity Gardens Estate 2 is a developed estate located inside Epe main Town in a very serene environment with close proximity to Epe Spa and Resorts, Alaro City, banks, markets, schools and various other developments. Some of the features of this amazing vicinity includes; Tarred roads, street light, clean portable water, drainage systems, perimeter fencing and a host of central sewage systems. Serenity Gardens set a high level benchmark in service delivery, infrastructures, eco-friendliness, functionality and loftiness. Saddled with Individual housing typologies of contemporary architecture.

The demographics of the area include a majority of Yoruba speaking natives, and people from different parts of the country living, working and doing business in the area. Epe town has potential for tourism as it is endowed with beautiful lagoon views and ocean fronts that will marvel your sight. The area is fast developing as investors and prospective land buyers are already building their homes and properties rapidly being one of the reasons why lands are constantly appreciating fast in the area.

Epe main town is a central hub for business, manufacturing, warehousing, and logistics. Forecasts have been made about an increase in commercial activities in this city as a result of these developments which will create thousands of jobs in the earnest future.

detail_description:
A tasteful and well finished 2 Bedroom Flats - All En-suite - for rent in a gated estate at Gbetu Awoyaya. It has Wardrobes and kitchen cabinets made with quality HDF woods. Customized room doors made with hard mahogany woods. steel entrance and back doors. water heaters in all rooms, water treatment system, each flat already wired for inverter, spacious compound, and adequately secured by estate security guards and a gate-man on the property, with perimeter CCTV surveillance. This is very suitable for a young couple; a bachelor or a spinster looking to stay in a cozy flat/apartment with adequate parking space, in a serene environment. Rent is N550,000/Annually. (Agency 10% and Agreement 10%). A refundable and Negotiable caution charge also apply.

PLEASE NOTE THE FOLLOWING ADDITIONAL DESCRIPTION before choosing to call us for inquiry:

Property is NOT by the express road. It's about an average of 8mins "slow" drive (i.e driving at a speed of 15KM/hr) from Lekki - Epe express way. ( might be lesser for a fast driver that is familiar with other alternative route in the area). And by Okada ride, its a N150 fare to the property location, from the major bus-stop "New Road Junction Bus Stop by Mayfair Garden. Notable landmarks before the bus stop ( coming from Ajah axis) are: Coscharis Motors, Greensprings Schools, Saphaire Estate, Meridian Park Estate etc. And as of a walking distance, it depends on individual's endurance "trecking" ability. The Road condition is average and NO flooding of any kind. NO INSPECTION FEE needed if coming on your own. Give us a call prior to coming for inspection, to enable us inform the security-men to allow you access through the estate entrance gate.

IMPORTANT: For new comers to Lagos or those who are not familiar with the Lekki-Epe express axis, Awoyaya is not in Songotedo or Abraham Adesanya or Ajah. Pls use your google map for more guide.

detail_description:
Serenity Gardens Estate 2 is a developed estate located inside Epe main Town in a very serene environment with close proximity to Epe Spa and Resorts, Alaro City, banks, markets, schools and various other developments. Some of the features of this amazing vicinity includes; Tarred roads, street light, clean portable water, drainage systems, perimeter fencing and a host of central sewage systems. Serenity Gardens set a high level benchmark in service delivery, infrastructures, eco-friendliness, functionality and loftiness. Saddled with Individual housing typologies of contemporary architecture.

The demographics of the area include a majority of Yoruba speaking natives, and people from different parts of the country living, working and doing business in the area. Epe town has potential for tourism as it is endowed with beautiful lagoon views and ocean fronts that will marvel your sight. The area is fast developing as investors and prospective land buyers are already building their homes and properties rapidly being one of the reasons why lands are constantly appreciating fast in the area.

Epe main town is a central hub for business, manufacturing, warehousing, and logistics. Forecasts have been made about an increase in commercial activities in this city as a result of these developments which will create thousands of jobs in the earnest future.

detail_description:
Serenity Gardens Estate 2 is a developed estate located inside Epe main Town in a very serene environment with close proximity to Epe Spa and Resorts, Alaro City, banks, markets, schools and various other developments. Some of the features of this amazing vicinity includes; Tarred roads, street light, clean portable water, drainage systems, perimeter fencing and a host of central sewage systems. Serenity Gardens set a high level benchmark in service delivery, infrastructures, eco-friendliness, functionality and loftiness. Saddled with Individual housing typologies of contemporary architecture.

The demographics of the area include a majority of Yoruba speaking natives, and people from different parts of the country living, working and doing business in the area. Epe town has potential for tourism as it is endowed with beautiful lagoon views and ocean fronts that will marvel your sight. The area is fast developing as investors and prospective land buyers are already building their homes and properties rapidly being one of the reasons why lands are constantly appreciating fast in the area.

Epe main town is a central hub for business, manufacturing, warehousing, and logistics. Forecasts have been made about an increase in commercial activities in this city as a result of these developments which will create thousands of jobs in the earnest future.

When it comes to land investment and development, it goes without saying that Lagos is one of the most appreciable places to buy, invest and make huge returns on your investment. A market trend on the popular real estate site, Nigria Property Centre, bears out this fact.

It is also evident that for the discerning investor, what is paramount is massive and optimal returns on any land investment made and when you come to Lagos, the best place to achieve massive growth in your land portfolio is Ibeju Lekki. Presently called the New Lagos, Ibeju Lekki is poised to become the most developed area in West Africa with the huge potential to be one of the best real estate decision you will ever make as countless developments are presently coming up within the axis.

King’s Gate 2 thus offers you the opportunity to key into the massive potentials in the Ibeju Lekki sector as it is a developed estate located at Imosan off Igbogun, via La Campaign Tropicana Resort, Free Trade Zone, Ibeju Lekki, Lagos with close proximity to The Dangote Refinery, Lekki Deep Seaport, La Campaign Tropicana, Lekki Golf Course, Alaro City, Eleganza Industries, Pan Atlantic University, Markets, Filling Stations and various other developments.

The Estate neighbourhood is presently populated with pockets of dwellers and investors readily building their properties. The estate is a prime land that will position your land portfolio for the next wave of dwellers and homeowners that are coming down to the area considering the economic catalysts within the Free Trade Zone axis such as the Dangote Refinery, Lekki Deep Sea Port, The Eleganza Industries, Alaro City and The New International Airport.

When it comes to land investment and development, it goes without saying that Lagos is one of the most appreciable places to buy, invest and make huge returns on your investment. A market trend on the popular real estate site, Nigria Property Centre, bears out this fact.

It is also evident that for the discerning investor, what is paramount is massive and optimal returns on any land investment made and when you come to Lagos, the best place to achieve massive growth in your land portfolio is Ibeju Lekki. Presently called the New Lagos, Ibeju Lekki is poised to become the most developed area in West Africa with the huge potential to be one of the best real estate decision you will ever make as countless developments are presently coming up within the axis.

King’s Gate 2 thus offers you the opportunity to key into the massive potentials in the Ibeju Lekki sector as it is a developed estate located at Imosan off Igbogun, via La Campaign Tropicana Resort, Free Trade Zone, Ibeju Lekki, Lagos with close proximity to The Dangote Refinery, Lekki Deep Seaport, La Campaign Tropicana, Lekki Golf Course, Alaro City, Eleganza Industries, Pan Atlantic University, Markets, Filling Stations and various other developments.

The Estate neighbourhood is presently populated with pockets of dwellers and investors readily building their properties. The estate is a prime land that will position your land portfolio for the next wave of dwellers and homeowners that are coming down to the area considering the economic catalysts within the Free Trade Zone axis such as the Dangote Refinery, Lekki Deep Sea Port, The Eleganza Industries, Alaro City and The New International Airport.

detail_description:
Serenity Gardens Estate 2 is a developed estate located inside Epe main Town in a very serene environment with close proximity to Epe Spa and Resorts, Alaro City, banks, markets, schools and various other developments. Some of the features of this amazing vicinity includes; Tarred roads, street light, clean portable water, drainage systems, perimeter fencing and a host of central sewage systems. Serenity Gardens set a high level benchmark in service delivery, infrastructures, eco-friendliness, functionality and loftiness. Saddled with Individual housing typologies of contemporary architecture.

The demographics of the area include a majority of Yoruba speaking natives, and people from different parts of the country living, working and doing business in the area. Epe town has potential for tourism as it is endowed with beautiful lagoon views and ocean fronts that will marvel your sight. The area is fast developing as investors and prospective land buyers are already building their homes and properties rapidly being one of the reasons why lands are constantly appreciating fast in the area.

Epe main town is a central hub for business, manufacturing, warehousing, and logistics. Forecasts have been made about an increase in commercial activities in this city as a result of these developments which will create thousands of jobs in the earnest future.

It is also evident that for the discerning investor, what is paramount is massive and optimal returns on any land investment made and when you come to Lagos, the best place to achieve massive growth in your land portfolio is Ibeju Lekki. Presently called the New Lagos, Ibeju Lekki is poised to become the most developed area in West Africa with the huge potential to be one of the best real estate decision you will ever make as countless developments are presently coming up within the axis.

King’s Gate 2 thus offers you the opportunity to key into the massive potentials in the Ibeju Lekki sector as it is a developed estate located at Imosan off Igbogun, via La Campaign Tropicana Resort, Free Trade Zone, Ibeju Lekki, Lagos with close proximity to The Dangote Refinery, Lekki Deep Seaport, La Campaign Tropicana, Lekki Golf Course, Alaro City, Eleganza Industries, Pan Atlantic University, Markets, Filling Stations and various other developments.

The Estate neighbourhood is presently populated with pockets of dwellers and investors readily building their properties. The estate is a prime land that will position your land portfolio for the next wave of dwellers and homeowners that are coming down to the area considering the economic catalysts within the Free Trade Zone axis such as the Dangote Refinery, Lekki Deep Sea Port, The Eleganza Industries, Alaro City and The New International Airport.

detail_description:
When it comes to land investment and development, it goes without saying that Lagos is one of the most appreciable places to buy, invest and make huge returns on your investment. A market trend on the popular real estate site, Nigria Property Centre, bears out this fact.

It is also evident that for the discerning investor, what is paramount is massive and optimal returns on any land investment made and when you come to Lagos, the best place to achieve massive growth in your land portfolio is Ibeju Lekki. Presently called the New Lagos, Ibeju Lekki is poised to become the most developed area in West Africa with the huge potential to be one of the best real estate decision you will ever make as countless developments are presently coming up within the axis.

King’s Gate 2 thus offers you the opportunity to key into the massive potentials in the Ibeju Lekki sector as it is a developed estate located at Imosan off Igbogun, via La Campaign Tropicana Resort, Free Trade Zone, Ibeju Lekki, Lagos with close proximity to The Dangote Refinery, Lekki Deep Seaport, La Campaign Tropicana, Lekki Golf Course, Alaro City, Eleganza Industries, Pan Atlantic University, Markets, Filling Stations and various other developments.

The Estate neighbourhood is presently populated with pockets of dwellers and investors readily building their properties. The estate is a prime land that will position your land portfolio for the next wave of dwellers and homeowners that are coming down to the area considering the economic catalysts within the Free Trade Zone axis such as the Dangote Refinery, Lekki Deep Sea Port, The Eleganza Industries, Alaro City and The New International Airport.

detail_description:
When it comes to land investment and development, it goes without saying that Lagos is one of the most appreciable places to buy, invest and make huge returns on your investment. A market trend on the popular real estate site, Nigria Property Centre, bears out this fact.

It is also evident that for the discerning investor, what is paramount is massive and optimal returns on any land investment made and when you come to Lagos, the best place to achieve massive growth in your land portfolio is Ibeju Lekki. detail_description:
When it comes to land investment and development, it goes without saying that Lagos is one of the most appreciable places to buy, invest and make huge returns on your investment. A market trend on the popular real estate site, Nigria Property Centre, bears out this fact.

It is also evident that for the discerning investor, what is paramount is massive and optimal returns on any land investment made and when you come to Lagos, the best place to achieve massive growth in your land portfolio is Ibeju Lekki. Presently called the New Lagos, Ibeju Lekki is poised to become the most developed area in West Africa with the huge potential to be one of the best real estate decision you will ever make as countless developments are presently coming up within the axis.

King’s Gate 2 thus offers you the opportunity to key into the massive potentials in the Ibeju Lekki sector as it is a developed estate located at Imosan off Igbogun, via La Campaign Tropicana Resort, Free Trade Zone, Ibeju Lekki, Lagos with close proximity to The Dangote Refinery, Lekki Deep Seaport, La Campaign Tropicana, Lekki Golf Course, Alaro City, Eleganza Industries, Pan Atlantic University, Markets, Filling Stations and various other developments.

The Estate neighbourhood is presently populated with pockets of dwellers and investors readily building their properties. The estate is a prime land that will position your land portfolio for the next wave of dwellers and homeowners that are coming down to the area considering the economic catalysts within the Free Trade Zone axis such as the Dangote Refinery, Lekki Deep Sea Port, The Eleganza Industries, Alaro City and The New International Airport.

King’s Gate 2 thus offers you the opportunity to key into the massive potentials in the Ibeju Lekki sector as it is a developed estate located at Imosan off Igbogun, via La Campaign Tropicana Resort, Free Trade Zone, Ibeju Lekki, Lagos with close proximity to The Dangote Refinery, Lekki Deep Seaport, La Campaign Tropicana, Lekki Golf Course, Alaro City, Eleganza Industries, Pan Atlantic University, Markets, Filling Stations and various other developments.

detail_description:
When it comes to land investment and development, it goes without saying that Lagos is one of the most appreciable places to buy, invest and make huge returns on your investment. A market trend on the popular real estate site, Nigria Property Centre, bears out this fact.

It is also evident that for the discerning investor, what is paramount is massive and optimal returns on any land investment made and when you come to Lagos, the best place to achieve massive growth in your land portfolio is Ibeju Lekki. Presently called the New Lagos, Ibeju Lekki is poised to become the most developed area in West Africa with the huge potential to be one of the best real estate decision you will ever make as countless developments are presently coming up within the axis.

King’s Gate 2 thus offers you the opportunity to key into the massive potentials in the Ibeju Lekki sector as it is a developed estate located at Imosan off Igbogun, via La Campaign Tropicana Resort, Free Trade Zone, Ibeju Lekki, Lagos with close proximity to The Dangote Refinery, Lekki Deep Seaport, La Campaign Tropicana, Lekki Golf Course, Alaro City, Eleganza Industries, Pan Atlantic University, Markets, Filling Stations and various other developments.

The Estate neighbourhood is presently populated with pockets of dwellers and investors readily building their properties. The estate is a prime land that will position your land portfolio for the next wave of dwellers and homeowners that are coming down to the area considering the economic catalysts within the Free Trade Zone axis such as the Dangote Refinery, Lekki Deep Sea Port, The Eleganza Industries, Alaro City and The New International Airport.

detail_description:
Serenity Gardens Estate 2 is a developed estate located inside Epe main Town in a very serene environment with close proximity to Epe Spa and Resorts, Alaro City, banks, markets, schools and various other developments. Some of the features of this amazing vicinity includes; Tarred roads, street light, clean portable water, drainage systems, perimeter fencing and a host of central sewage systems. Serenity Gardens set a high level benchmark in service delivery, infrastructures, eco-friendliness, functionality and loftiness. Saddled with Individual housing typologies of contemporary architecture.

The demographics of the area include a majority of Yoruba speaking natives, and people from different parts of the country living, working and doing business in the area. Epe town has potential for tourism as it is endowed with beautiful lagoon views and ocean fronts that will marvel your sight. The area is fast developing as investors and prospective land buyers are already building their homes and properties rapidly being one of the reasons why lands are constantly appreciating fast in the area.

Epe main town is a central hub for business, manufacturing, warehousing, and logistics. Forecasts have been made about an increase in commercial activities in this city as a result of these developments which will create thousands of jobs in the earnest future.

detail_description:
When it comes to land investment and development, it goes without saying that Lagos is one of the most appreciable places to buy, invest and make huge returns on your investment. A market trend on the popular real estate site, Nigria Property Centre, bears out this fact.

It is also evident that for the discerning investor, what is paramount is massive and optimal returns on any land investment made and when you come to Lagos, the best place to achieve massive growth in your land portfolio is Ibeju Lekki. Presently called the New Lagos, Ibeju Lekki is poised to become the most developed area in West Africa with the huge potential to be one of the best real estate decision you will ever make as countless developments are presently coming up within the axis.

detail_description:
Serenity Gardens Estate 2 is a developed estate located inside Epe main Town in a very serene environment with close proximity to Epe Spa and Resorts, Alaro City, banks, markets, schools and various other developments. Some of the features of this amazing vicinity includes; Tarred roads, street light, clean portable water, drainage systems, perimeter fencing and a host of central sewage systems. Serenity Gardens set a high level benchmark in service delivery, infrastructures, eco-friendliness, functionality and loftiness. Saddled with Individual housing typologies of contemporary architecture.

The demographics of the area include a majority of Yoruba speaking natives, and people from different parts of the country living, working and doing business in the area. Epe town has potential for tourism as it is endowed with beautiful lagoon views and ocean fronts that will marvel your sight. The area is fast developing as investors and prospective land buyers are already building their homes and properties rapidly being one of the reasons why lands are constantly appreciating fast in the area.

Epe main town is a central hub for business, manufacturing, warehousing, and logistics. Forecasts have been made about an increase in commercial activities in this city as a result of these developments which will create thousands of jobs in the earnest future.

detail_description:
Serenity Gardens Estate 2 is a developed estate located inside Epe main Town in a very serene environment with close proximity to Epe Spa and Resorts, Alaro City, banks, markets, schools and various other developments. Some of the features of this amazing vicinity includes; Tarred roads, street light, clean portable water, drainage systems, perimeter fencing and a host of central sewage systems. Serenity Gardens set a high level benchmark in service delivery, infrastructures, eco-friendliness, functionality and loftiness. Saddled with Individual housing typologies of contemporary architecture.

The demographics of the area include a majority of Yoruba speaking natives, and people from different parts of the country living, working and doing business in the area. Epe town has potential for tourism as it is endowed with beautiful lagoon views and ocean fronts that will marvel your sight. The area is fast developing as investors and prospective land buyers are already building their homes and properties rapidly being one of the reasons why lands are constantly appreciating fast in the area.

Epe main town is a central hub for business, manufacturing, warehousing, and logistics. Forecasts have been made about an increase in commercial activities in this city as a result of these developments which will create thousands of jobs in the earnest future.

detail_description:
When it comes to land investment and development, it goes without saying that Lagos is one of the most appreciable places to buy, invest and make huge returns on your investment. A market trend on the popular real estate site, Nigria Property Centre, bears out this fact.

It is also evident that for the discerning investor, what is paramount is massive and optimal returns on any land investment made and when you come to Lagos, the best place to achieve massive growth in your land portfolio is Ibeju Lekki. Presently called the New Lagos, Ibeju Lekki is poised to become the most developed area in West Africa with the huge potential to be one of the best real estate decision you will ever make as countless developments are presently coming up within the axis.

King’s Gate 2 thus offers you the opportunity to key into the massive potentials in the Ibeju Lekki sector as it is a developed estate located at Imosan off Igbogun, via La Campaign Tropicana Resort, Free Trade Zone, Ibeju Lekki, Lagos with close proximity to The Dangote Refinery, Lekki Deep Seaport, La Campaign Tropicana, Lekki Golf Course, Alaro City, Eleganza Industries, Pan Atlantic University, Markets, Filling Stations and various other developments.

The Estate neighbourhood is presently populated with pockets of dwellers and investors readily building their properties. The estate is a prime land that will position your land portfolio for the next wave of dwellers and homeowners that are coming down to the area considering the economic catalysts within the Free Trade Zone axis such as the Dangote Refinery, Lekki Deep Sea Port, The Eleganza Industries, Alaro City and The New International Airport.

When it comes to land investment and development, it goes without saying that Lagos is one of the most appreciable places to buy, invest and make huge returns on your investment. A market trend on the popular real estate site, Nigria Property Centre, bears out this fact.

It is also evident that for the discerning investor, what is paramount is massive and optimal returns on any land investment made and when you come to Lagos, the best place to achieve massive growth in your land portfolio is Ibeju Lekki. Presently called the New Lagos, Ibeju Lekki is poised to become the most developed area in West Africa with the huge potential to be one of the best real estate decision you will ever make as countless developments are presently coming up within the axis.

King’s Gate 2 thus offers you the opportunity to key into the massive potentials in the Ibeju Lekki sector as it is a developed estate located at Imosan off Igbogun, via La Campaign Tropicana Resort, Free Trade Zone, Ibeju Lekki, Lagos with close proximity to The Dangote Refinery, Lekki Deep Seaport, La Campaign Tropicana, Lekki Golf Course, Alaro City, Eleganza Industries, Pan Atlantic University, Markets, Filling Stations and various other developments.

The Estate neighbourhood is presently populated with pockets of dwellers and investors readily building their properties. The estate is a prime land that will position your land portfolio for the next wave of dwellers and homeowners that are coming down to the area considering the economic catalysts within the Free Trade Zone axis such as the Dangote Refinery, Lekki Deep Sea Port, The Eleganza Industries, Alaro City and The New International Airport.

detail_description:
Serenity Gardens Estate 2 is a developed estate located inside Epe main Town in a very serene environment with close proximity to Epe Spa and Resorts, Alaro City, banks, markets, schools and various other developments. Some of the features of this amazing vicinity includes; Tarred roads, street light, clean portable water, drainage systems, perimeter fencing and a host of central sewage systems. Serenity Gardens set a high level benchmark in service delivery, infrastructures, eco-friendliness, functionality and loftiness. Saddled with Individual housing typologies of contemporary architecture.

The demographics of the area include a majority of Yoruba speaking natives, and people from different parts of the country living, working and doing business in the area. Epe town has potential for tourism as it is endowed with beautiful lagoon views and ocean fronts that will marvel your sight. The area is fast developing as investors and prospective land buyers are already building their homes and properties rapidly being one of the reasons why lands are constantly appreciating fast in the area.

Epe main town is a central hub for business, manufacturing, warehousing, and logistics. Forecasts have been made about an increase in commercial activities in this city as a result of these developments which will create thousands of jobs in the earnest future.
